trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.AnchorChanged" /> and <see cref="E:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.CargoChanged" /> events.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="E:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.AnchorChanged" /> 和 <see cref="E:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.CargoChanged" /> 事件的資料。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventArgs> data includes the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation> that raised the event, the anchor or cargo resource associated with the event, and the action that was taken - <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Added>, <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Removed>, or <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Modified>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventArgs>資料包括<xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation>，會引發事件，並採取的動作相關聯的事件、 錨點或貨物資源<xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Added>， <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Removed>，或<xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Modified>。

trans-unit.source: The annotation that raised the event.
The <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors" /> or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos" /> resource of the event.
trans-unit.target: 事件的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors" /> 或 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos" /> 資源。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="M:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventArgs.#ctor(System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation,System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction,System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource)" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="M:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventArgs.#ctor(System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation,System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction,System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource)" /> 類別的新執行個體。
<paramref name="annotation" /> 或 <paramref name="action" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="action" /> is not a valid <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction" /> value.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="action" /> 不是有效的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction" /> 值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the action of the annotation <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventArgs.Resource" />.

The <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResourceChangedEventHandler> is called when an <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> resource is <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Added>, <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Removed>, or <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Modified>.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation" /> that raised the event.
Gets the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors" /> or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos" /> resource associated with the event.
trans-unit.target: 取得與事件關聯的 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors" /> 或 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos" /> 資源。

trans-unit.source: The annotation anchor or cargo resource that was <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Added" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Removed" />, or <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Modified" />.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Added" />、<see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Removed" />，或 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationAction.Modified" /> 的附註錨定或貨物資源。
